! Colors
! Special colors
*.foreground: #ABB2BF
*.background: #1E2127
*.cursorColor: #5C6370
! black
*.color0: #1E2127
*.color8: #4C6370
! red
*.color1: #E06C75
*.color9: #E06C75
! green
*.color2: #98C379
*.color10: #98C379
! yellow
*.color3: #D19A66
*.color11: #D19A66
! blue
